5. Business Requirements 5.1 Functional Requirements
1. Lead Management
o Capture leads from multiple sources (manual entry, website, referral)
o Lead assignment to agents
o Lead status tracking (New → Contacted → Quoted → Converted/Closed)
2. Customer Management
o Maintain customer master database
o Store demographic details, contact info, and identification documents o Policy history and interaction log
3. Policy Management
o Create and track policy applications
o Manage renewals, lapses, and endorsements o Automated reminders for policy renewals
4. Customer Service Module
o Ticket creation for customer complaints/queries o Ticket assignment and escalation
o SLA monitoring and resolution tracking
5. Reporting and Analytics
o Sales pipeline dashboard
o Agent performance reports
o Policy sales and renewal reports o Customer service SLA reports
6. Integration Requirements
o Email/SMS service integration
o Document upload and storage system
5.2 Non-functional Requirements
• Usability: Intuitive UI for non-technical users
• Performance: System should support 500+ concurrent users
• Security: Role-based access, data encryption, audit logs
• Scalability: Ability to onboard new agents and departments
• Availability: 99.5% system uptime
